{"word":"G3443 - μονόω - monóō - mon-o'-o - Be desolate","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μονόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">monóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mon-o'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be desolate</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தனிமையாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to make single or solitary; to leave alone, forsake"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3441 - μόνος - mónos - mon'-os/3441\">G3441</a>; to <i>isolate</i>, that is, <i>bereave:</i> - be desolate.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3439/3439\">G3439</a>, <a href=\"#/G3440/3440\">G3440</a>, <a href=\"#/G3441/3441\">G3441</a>, <a href=\"#/G3442/3442\">G3442</a>, <a href=\"#/G3443/3443\">G3443</a>"}]}